Third-party software (runtime)

The CS2Helper `gsi-cli` application may download and run **PresentMon**
(<https://github.com/GameTechDev/PresentMon>) from official GitHub releases on
Windows for frame-timing / presentation telemetry. PresentMon is not part of
this repository; it is separate software.

PresentMon is licensed under the MIT License, Copyright (C) 2017-2024 Intel
Corporation. Its terms and full license text are available in the upstream
repository. Your use of PresentMon is governed by that license, not by the
license above, which applies to the CS2Helper project’s own source code.
